The dlmalloc engine in libc/src/dlmalloc/malloc.c is upstream Doug Lea
v2.8.6 (released to the public domain). The file's top comment cites
the canonical CC0 release statement:

    This is a version (aka dlmalloc) of malloc/free/realloc written by
